e  shut down margin trading in 2020.) But your competitors probably offer l=
oans, and it is tempting for you to do it too. So you say, sure, fine, I=E2=
=80=99ll take your $10,000 and put $20,000 of Bitcoin in your account.
But where do you get the money that you are lending to the customer? Well, =
you have to borrow it too. Ordinarily the way that you will borrow it is by=
