=C2=A0You have to pay Customer B out of your own capital, and you don=E2=80=
=99t get it back from Customer A. You've just lost money. Actually that=E2=
=80=99s the best outcome. The worst outcome is that you don=E2=80=99t have =
enough capital, you go bankrupt, and Customer B does not get his money back=
.
Everyone knows=C2=A0this, which is why crypto exchanges =E2=80=94=C2=A0and =
securities broker-dealers, who have the same basic business model =E2=80=94=
=C2=A0spend most of their time thinking about risk management. Before the p=
