get you in trouble.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But sometimes market moves are catastrophic, a=
nd in particular, sometimes securities broker-dealers and crypto exchanges =
will have =E2=80=9Crun on the bank=E2=80=9D risks. If everyone knows that y=
ou are in this situation =E2=80=94=C2=A0that you have a lot of Bitcoin coll=
ateral and Bitcoin prices are falling =E2=80=94=C2=A0people will expect you=
 to have to liquidate your Bitcoin collateral, so they will expect Bitcoin =
prices to fall, so they will sell Bitcoin, which will cause Bitcoin prices =
to fall, which will cause your long-Bitcoin customers to default, which wil=
l cause you to liquidate Bitcoin at lower and lower prices, etc., until you=
 are bankrupt.</p>
