 now-worthless FTT. Also the fact that Customer C had all that FTT in the f=
irst place is not a great sign. It is an FTT whale, and FTT is now worthles=
s. Has it been borrowing elsewhere against FTT? Are all those debts coming =
due?=C2=A0</p>
