y the way I have outlined.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">One other point here is that if this is the st=
ory, then it is not a=C2=A0<em>liquidity=C2=A0</em>crisis but a=C2=A0<em>so=
lvency=C2=A0</em>one. That is, the problem is not a timing mismatch, in whi=
ch FTX=E2=80=99s customers asked for their cash back but FTX did not have e=
nough ready cash because it had long-term but money-good loans out. The pro=
blem is that FTX took its customers=E2=80=99 money and traded it for a pile=
